@url=http://localhost:3000

### Seed fake data (clears and seeds all tables)
POST {{url}}/faker

### Create a user
POST {{url}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "email": "jane.doe@example.com",
  "password": "securePassword123",
  "role": "CUSTOMER"
}

### Get all users
GET {{url}}/users

### Get a user by id
GET {{url}}/users/:id

### Update a user
PUT {{url}}/users/:id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Updated",
  "email": "jane.updated@example.com"
}

### Delete a user
DELETE {{url}}/users/:id

